data.description: Private 2-bedroom home with over a 1-acre lot. The home and garage has a newer metal roof, fresh painted cabinets, updated hardware and a new backsplash in the kitchen. Updated bathrooms, replaced sewer drain in the basement. Gas Fireplace in the family room, 1 stall garage in the basement, lots of extra storage space. Great porch the length of the house, a small deck on the back of the house. 26x34 detached garage. Carport to store your extra equipment. Invisible fencing around the property for your dogs. Concrete driveway. If you're looking to downsize but want some land, this is the property for you. Close to all the amenities in McConnelsville.
